goyenda gogol ( or goenda gogol ; english : detective gogol , bengali : গোয়েন্দা গোগোল ) is a 2013 indian bengali suspense film , directed by arindam dey and produced by supratik ghosh under the banner of ishani films . based on the story sonali parer rahashya by samaresh basu , the film features child actor ahijit ghosh and indraneil sengupta in the lead roles . it boasts of being the first film to feature a tattooed bengali private detective ( indraneil sengupta ) . saheb chatterjee and rachana banerjee also play parents for the first time in this film . the film was released on 24 may 2013 .